Story

Quick Teria Writeup because I totally forgot.

 

Teria is from a royal family in Water Deep, but she only uses that in dire circumstances. Like people are about to die type situations.

 

A few years ago Teria and her sister became pirates. They choose who they are going to rob and steal from by a list of really bad people. They have been very good at this profession too, up until they were pirated.

 

Their father thinks they are selling their family wines. He didn’t like this idea at first, but thought, “Maybe this will help them be more diplomatic” so he helped them on their endeavors. They use this as a cover.

 

Teria and a water genasi Shoalar used to work together. They had a … ummm… falling out. Shoalar was the one that stole the boat from her. He now rolls with a different band of pirates. (Teria felt like leaving that last part out).
